    "name": "Eyes Over Us",
    "steam_appid": 1819660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/3a9ed233797175fa7c0a132df638b6b1.avif?t=1699284595\" width=500 height=157 /></span><br><br>《Eyes Over Us》是一款超现实程序生成叙事策略游戏，你将扮演一个洛夫克拉夫特式的实体，监视两个正在接受实验的人类。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2></strong><br><br>作为一个洛夫克拉夫特式的实体，你通过痛苦、磨难和疯狂影响受害者，而不是直接控制他们。改变思想，身体很快就会随之改变。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/4e6dbc90c62d1f921fd82f8ec5ee68ab.poster.avif?t=1699284595\" width=500 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/4e6dbc90c62d1f921fd82f8ec5ee68ab.webm?t=1699284595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/4e6dbc90c62d1f921fd82f8ec5ee68ab.mp4?t=1699284595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一款实验性游戏，因此，你会发现事物运作方式的众多奥秘。实验和许多启示很快就会随之而来。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >图形</h2></strong><br><br>通过极简主义、美丽而怪异的转描动画镜头看世界，这些动画由真人制作（已征得同意），而不是在酷刑室内制作而成。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/a2f9a3ad4817e37188bd096d464773a3.poster.avif?t=1699284595\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/a2f9a3ad4817e37188bd096d464773a3.webm?t=1699284595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819660/extras/a2f9a3ad4817e37188bd096d464773a3.mp4?t=1699284595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
